    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-02-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-02-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="515" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d515">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">White</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-02-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 13,
                                    1894</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>(Received February 28.)</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 189.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to your dispatch 149, relative
                            to the alleged assistance of Jewish emigrants to the United States, I
                            have the honor to inform you that I have this day received a note from
                            the imperial foreign office stating that this report is absolutely
                            without foundation.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Andrew D. White.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
